code: /**  * Returns an initializable for an instance that requires no initialization.  */ static <T> Initializable<T> of(final T instance) {     return new Initializable<T>() {          @Override         public T get(Errors errors) throws ErrorsException {             return instance.         }          @Override         public String toString() {             return String.valueOf(instance).         }     }. }
